title: Practicing The Basics Is the Key To Weightloss
itunes:title: Practicing The Basics Is the Key To Weightloss
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

In this podcast we go deep talking about the difference between consuming information and taking action. 

We also talk about what happens when you practice your new tools again and again and again. You make mistakes! Mistakes are essential to finding your way. Without making mistakes, you don't open your mind to finding the answers and to figuring things out.
